1.Initial phase
       It is defining the value of state and props
2.Mounting phasee
    a.constructor()--> used to construct a class component 
    b.getDerivedStateFromProps()-->used to get the value from state and proprs
    c.render()--->used to render the components over the browser/ used to render the webpage
    d.componentDidMount()--<used to work with the side effect[i.e:HTTP request]

3.Updating phase
    a.getDerivedStateFromProps()==>used to get the value from state and props
    b.shouldComponentUpdate()==>used to declare whether component should update or not?
    c.render()==>used to render the webpage
    d.getSnapshotBeforeUpdate()==>used to store the previous state and props values
    e.componentDidUpdate()==>used to work with side effects 